24.64165130097433, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [15, 298]}], "orig": "Lake Elemtaita Our wedding grounds venue can accommodate 150 guests, with its lush green lawn that brings out the truly outdoor wedding event. With the best green grounds to be found on the shores of Lake Elementaita , the Sawela Capella Lodge is an ideal wedding venue among destinations in Kenya.", "text": "Lake Elemtaita Our wedding grounds venue can accommodate 150 guests, with its lush green lawn that brings out the truly outdoor wedding event. With the best green grounds to be found on the shores of Lake Elementaita , the Sawela Capella Lodge is an ideal wedding venue among destinations in Kenya."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/2", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 3, "bbox": {"l": 19.317862235089038, "t": 281.0318552575094, "r": 235.71217015832536, "b": 213.24648494942267, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 134]}], "orig": "A luxurious, spacious restaurant with a 70pax capacity, offering a variety of delicacies crafted from the finest seasonal ingredients.", "text": "A luxurious, spacious restaurant with a 70pax capacity, offering a variety of delicacies crafted from the finest seasonal ingredients."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/3", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 3, "bbox": {"l": 19.317862235089038, "t": 187.44096715712993, "r": 220.3084324791448, "b": 138.3737744691191, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 105]}], "orig": "Guests can also enjoy breathtaking outdoor views, making it the perfect place for a delightful breakfast.", "text": "Guests can also enjoy breathtaking outdoor views, making it the perfect place for a delightful breakfast."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/4", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 3, "bbox": {"l": 278.0841100131616, "t": 206.79627937998828, "r": 497.33113321086864, "b": 129.05944346895308, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 113]}], "orig": "We have a specious well-furnished family style lounge area fitted with a smart Tv and a family friendly bar area.", "text": "We have a specious well-furnished family style lounge area fitted with a smart Tv and a family friendly bar area."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/5", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 4, "bbox": {"l": 12.89894850254379, "t": 200.44030264482058, "r": 498.8111692937004, "b": 113.78969546538218, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 414]}], "orig": "At Sawela Capella Lodge, we offer versatile conference and event facilities in a serene lakeside setting. Whether you're hosting a seminar, workshop, or corporate conference, our well-equipped venues provide the ideal environment for productivity and success. With a range of customizable services and professional support, we ensure seamless planning and execution, making your event both impactful and memorable.", "text": "At Sawela Capella Lodge, we offer versatile conference and event facilities in a serene lakeside setting. Whether you're hosting a seminar, workshop, or corporate conference, our well-equipped venues provide the ideal environment for productivity and success. With a range of customizable services and professional support, we ensure seamless planning and execution, making your event both impactful and memorable."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/6", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/0"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 5, "bbox": {"l": 37.68903841962333, "t": 258.9754909093544, "r": 229.73184289283952, "b": 176.07937595577636, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 171]}], "orig": "Enjoy our 24-hour naturally heated swimming pool with a jacuzzi by the pool side, surrounded by lush, wellgroomed gardens-perfect for events, teambuilding and photoshoots.", "text": "Enjoy our 24-hour naturally heated swimming pool with a jacuzzi by the pool side, surrounded by lush, wellgroomed gardens-perfect for events, teambuilding and photoshoots.", "enumerated": false, "marker": ""}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/7", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/0"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 5, "bbox": {"l": 37.68903841962333, "t": 168.97549465935435, "r": 240.12869735963724, "b": 86.07937970577643, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 163]}], "orig": "We offer a variety of fun and energetic activities for all ages, including Blloon Safaris, trampoline, boardgames like chess and scrabble, archery and PlayStation.", "text": "We offer a variety of fun and energetic activities for all ages, including Blloon Safaris, trampoline, boardgames like chess and scrabble, archery and PlayStation.", "enumerated": false, "marker": ""}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/8", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 6, "bbox": {"l": 314.2169518976265, "t": 273.3437889591403, "r": 452.0568329834231, "b": 209.7647678752262, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 11]}], "orig": "contact us:", "text": "contact us:"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/9", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 6, "bbox": {"l": 324.02585890392197, "t": 185.00994865408563, "r": 437.1776343228611, "b": 109.70001788374111, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 32]}], "orig": "0729811507 0742000222 0708000111", "text": "0729811507 0742000222 0708000111"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/10", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 6, "bbox": {"l": 289.76358181951696, "t": 99.5767382618028, "r": 471.4250360436515, "b": 81.2222810863135, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 18]}], "orig": "@sawelacapellaloge", "tex